<TITLE>
The Woodsman (Wood Man), Wild Man of the Athabaskan tribes
</TITLE>

<META NAME="description" CONTENT="Information and legends about the Native American mythological figure Wood Man
(or the Woodsman), an Athabaskan wild man of the forest.">
<meta charset="utf-8"/> 				

