<a name="lore">Woodsman Stories</a>
</u></H2>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://jukebox.uaf.edu/RavenStory/htm/jjpc.htm
">The Wild Woman</a>:</b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Two Koyukon elders telling the story of a woman who became a Woodsman.
